<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
13:25
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='794254' id='t-794254'>Principle number four:</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='797079' id='t-797079'>we should take about
a quarter of the Earth</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='799780' id='t-799780'>and only let Darwin run the show there.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='802981' id='t-802981'>It doesn't have to be contiguous,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='804606' id='t-804606'>doesn't have to all be tied together.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='806404' id='t-806404'>It should be part
in the oceans, part on land.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='808634' id='t-808634'>But we should not run every
evolutionary decision on this planet.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='812474' id='t-812474'>We want to have
our evolutionary system running.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='814936' id='t-814936'>We want to have Darwin's
evolutionary system running.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='817537' id='t-817537'>And it's just really important to have
these two things running in parallel</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='821237' id='t-821237'>and not overwhelm evolution.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
13:53
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='822778' id='t-822778'>(Applause)</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
14:01
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='830307' id='t-830307'>Last thing I'll say.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='832654' id='t-832654'>This is the single most exciting
adventure human beings have been on.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='835940' id='t-835940'>This is the single greatest superpower
