<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='841897' id='t-841897'>because you're scared of it,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='843333' id='t-843333'>because you're hiding from it.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='845096' id='t-845096'>You can participate in the ethics.
